Harper Says ‘Facts’ Don’t Support Massive Expansion of Deficits

-- B y   T h e o p h i l o s   A r g i t i s
-- 
2011-09-29T18:29:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/harper-says-facts-don-t-support-massive-expansion-of-deficits.html
Canadian Prime Minister  Stephen
Harper  says the “facts” don’t support “massively” expanding
the country’s budget deficit.  Harper made the comments to lawmakers in Ottawa.  To contact the reporter on this story:
